fondly - Privacy Policy
Last Updated: December 22, 2024
Welcome to fondly! This Privacy Policy describes how Connected Media ("us", "we", or "our") handles information in connection with the fondly mobile application (the "App").
1. No Collection of Personal Information
fondly does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users.
The App does not require any user registration or login, and does not track your location.
2. Data Storage
Your quiz answers are stored locally on your device and are deleted when you delete the app. Any answers you view or generate using the app are never sent to our server or seen by us.
3. No Third-Party Access
We do not share any information with third parties, as we do not collect any data that can be shared.
4. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
5. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
help@connectedmedia.co
.